reviews.text: The restaurant locates in commercial district where the walking distance from the Kowloon Bay MTR station is about 15 mins.  Actually, it is not difficult to find it though it is not near the shopping malls.  The restaurant is quite big and spacious as it has high ceiling and there are sufficient spaces between chairs.  I felt comfortable to have lunch here.  The staff served every customer a small bowl of porridge for free.  It contains dried tofu curds, carrots, taros, peanuts, black-eyed pea and ginger.  The taste was sweet and the texture was thick.  I felt warm because of the ginger.  Lunch set has soup, side dish and main course at $53 plus 10% services charge.  The portion of the main course was large.  The price is quite fair for the whole set of lunch and porridge which made me fully satisfied.  I chose Taiwan marinated bean curd with five-spice powder sauce which was tasty and juicy.  I came here for this.  I chose Taiwan fried rice noodle for the main course which had mushrooms and vegetables only, it's simple but the taste was also good.
Good place to have lunch,  although few set lunch chose,  but the food served are very delicious,  must try the veggie Barbecued pork!

Went there for lunch today with a friend around 12:40pm. We ordered the lunch set with exactly the same main dish (BBQ pork) except for the side dish (she ordered kimchi and I ordered tofu).

Hers came pretty soon and I waited for more than 30 minutes. Despite couple of attempts to ask what took the kitchen so long to prepare the same lunch set, their response was, ' the kitchen messed up with the orders'. 

I sat right next to the kitchen and I saw no one going into the kitchen and asked about my lunch set, which I presumed it should not take long to put  together a few pieces of BBQ pork with some white rice.

I told them to cancel my order. By the time my friend finished her meal, mine came with the wrong side dish. When we walked out to the cashier, we saw the restaurant was not completely full.

Summary: Bad management, bad services and ridiculously slow.
It's good for vegetarians.
Excellent restaurant though little bit costly. I was happy to see good amount of Bhuddhist monks also taking food.Food was really excellent.Good place for vegans especially non-Indian Veg food.

大集團的發展項目。
高級商廈？低級泊車操作？今時今日仲玩泊車留匙！架車出咗事！唔見嘢又話閣下自理！
那裡有中國運動品牌---特步辦事處，有很多特製波鞋展示
